        <div class="about-photo-wrapper reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <img src="/shared/NathanFrame.jpg" class="about-photo" alt="Nathan Carpenter" width="506" height="675" loading="lazy" asp-append-version="true" />
        </div>

        <div class="about-paragraphs reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <p>My experience spans a wide range of technologies, providing me with a solid foundation across networking, cloud, and enterprise IT.</p>

            <ul class="about-highlights">
                <li><span class="highlight-tag">Network Architecture</span> firewalls, routing &amp; switching, virtual networking</li>
                <li><span class="highlight-tag">System Administration</span> Windows Server, virtualization</li>
                <li><span class="highlight-tag">Identity &amp; Access</span> Entra ID, Intune</li>
                <li><span class="highlight-tag">Automation</span> PowerShell scripting</li>
                <li><span class="highlight-tag">Cloud (Azure)</span> Virtual Networks, Virtual Machines, App Services</li>
            </ul>

